<br>
1) Make it so it can only be used on mobs with HPs of 20% or lower. <br>
or<br>
2) Make it so it can only be used when mobs are Enraged or after they Enrage.<br>
<br>
Here is another idea I had today lets call it Atomicburn =p<br>
It would do damage based on the casters total hps (includings buffs) + total mana. The drawback of this skill would be death.<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p>Kaplowee Kablamo<br>
Wizard of the 65th nuke<br>
Dark Horizon of Zebuxoruk<br>
