<br>
<br>
The other idea is [u]much[/u] more interesting though. I have thought about some form of sacrifice spell for other classes too. For Enchanters i thought of something like a huge, 2 minute, unresistable mezz for mobs lvl 65 and below, at the extend of the Enchanter though. Or for Necromancers a sort-of-banish, which takes BOTH the mob and the necro as a price. And it takes the Necromancers corpse to his bind spot too - so you cannot simply rezz him back into the raid. (name ideas: Enchanter Skill Wrath of Eternity, Necromancer skill Call of Death)<br>
<br>
